    Implements some empty versions of non-obligatory methods.
    Algorithm
    An Algorithm has to provide a function that returns an array of Parameters it needs, in order to give user interfaces the possibility to provide the Algorithm with appropriate.
    Category
    An enum containing a set of categories for algorithms These fixed categories enable possiblities of grouping and searching algorithms Algorithms can be part of multiple categories
